org.apache.tephra.persist

Class AbstractTransactionLog

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.tephra.persist.AbstractTransactionLog
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    TransactionLog
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    HDFSTransactionLog, LocalFileTransactionLog

    public abstract class AbstractTransactionLog
extends Object
implements TransactionLog
    Common implementation of a transaction log, backed by file reader and writer based storage. Classes extending this class, must also implement TransactionLogWriter and TransactionLogReader.
